---
title: Mushroom Ravioli and Salmon in Parmesan Sauce with Balsamic Tomatoes and Buttery Panko Topping
description: This earthy mushroom ravioli dinner is an absolute umami bomb! The flavours of salmon, mushrooms, Parmesan and juicy, balsamic-glazed tomatoes unite for a truly showstopping meal.
